## Tailwind

If Tailwind library not installed already, install it according to https://docs.astro.build/en/guides/styling/#tailwind

Global styles in src/styles/global.css must be wrapped in @layer to not override Tailwind styles.

## SVG

Inline svg icons have to be extracted to src/icons as .astro components and imported on the page.
Guide for svg: https://docs.astro.build/en/guides/images/#svg-components

## Directories structure and imports

- src/components/ - Reusable components that repeats on one or multiple pages
- src/icons/ - SVG icons
- src/layouts/ - Base layouts used for group of pages with same base layout but different content
- src/pages/ - Separate pages on the site
- src/styles/ - Global styles
  - src/styles/<page_name> - Pages styles when styles on the page are over 200 lines of code

## Base Layout

If base layout included in prompt then skip existing in layout parts on the destination page.

## Verification

Verify in IDE browser that destination is exactly the same with source
